    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Domni <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Marquis/duke #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            ref="#people/3002">Iordanis</persName> divina ordinante clementia
                        Capuanorum <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs> petitioni dilecti sui clementer
                        favet. Notum sit omnibus sancte et catholice Ecclesie filiis <persName
                            key="#Princeps #parentOf" ref="#people/3001">Richardum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principem</rs>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">patrem</rs> meum, quia cognovit locum qui dicitur ad
                            <placeName ref="#places/2803">Arcum Diane</placeName>, in quo ecclesia
                            <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Inflow #Churches #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3046">Sancti Angeli</orgName> constructa est,
                        utilem ad congregationem <rs key="#Monks">monachorum</rs> et construendum
                            <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs>, angustum tamen, adeo quod non
                        erat amplius quam ecclesia nuper constructa accingit et officina monachorum,
                        dedisse pro eo in <rs key="#Commutatio">commutationem</rs>
                        <persName key="#Archbishops" ref="#people/3063">Ildebrando</persName>
                        Capuano <rs key="#Archbishops">archiepiscopo</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs> magnam constructam in <placeName
                            ref="#places/173" key="#Cities">Capuam</placeName>, vocabulo <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3050"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Outflow #Counter-gift #Luxury #Books #Churches"
                            >Sancti Iohannis Areppaldi</orgName>, ditatam <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris multis</rs> et <rs key="#Luxury"
                            >ornamentis</rs> et <rs key="#Books">libris</rs>, et recepit in
                        commutationem ipsam ecclesiam Sancti Angeli ad Arcum Diane et aliam <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Gift #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3063">Sancti Angeli constructam in Capuam, que
                            nuncupatur de Odaldisci</orgName>. Et quia pro suo tempore religiosus
                        ille locus cepit augmentari, additis suis rebus secundum quod placuit, quam
                        maxime crevit. Quapropter a me et ab <rs key="#marriage">uxore</rs> mea
                        locus ille valde diligitur, Die quadam ego prescriptus Iordanus princeps,
                        divina inspiratione compulsus, ivi ad prescriptam ecclesiam Sancti Angeli ad
                        Arcum Diane causa orationis, et religiosorum <rs key="#Intercessory"
                            >plurimorum monachorum a me postulavit</rs> prudentia, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Other_clerics #Monks"><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Iohannis</name></persName> scilicet <rs key="#Monks">monachi</rs>
                        et <rs key="#Other_clerics">decani</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Monks" ref="#people/4241">Maynardi</persName> et
                            <persName key="#Intercessory #Monks"><name ref="Petrus"
                            >Petri</name></persName> et aliorurn <rs key="#Monks">monachorum</rs>,
                        quatenus per firmitatis apices concederem monasterio que possidebant et
                        dominabantur. Quorum precibus favens, per huius concessionis paginam concedo
                        que princeps Richardus pater meus dedit et que ego postea tribui et que
                        eidem pertinent monasterio et que possidebat e dominabantur. Illius vero
                        loci <rs key="#Fines">fines</rs> primum indico sic concedens: ex una parte
                        sunt cave cimentaree qualiter pergitur per <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3818">Sancti
                            Marcelli</orgName> et ad terram que dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/4551">Bertarisci</placeName>, et qualiter redit per latera
                        montis et per ipsas criptas et ascendit inde per canalem qui dicitur ad
                        Ficum Fusculam et qualiter redit per ipsam viam antiquam et per Rickibellum
                        et qualiter descendit per latera Calvini et per terram <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/2321">Sancti Benedicti
                            constructi in Capuam</orgName> et qualiter descendit per terram <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3033">Sancti Vincentii</orgName> usque ad cavas
                        cimentarias. Et concedo quicquid continetur in cartula oblationis quod pater
                        meus prescriptus obtulit eiusdem monasterio Sancti Angeli, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            ref="#places/4528">Sarzanum</placeName> et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants"
                            >homines</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >terras</rs> a <placeName ref="#places/4529"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Coloni/tenants">Sancto Martino qui dicitur ad
                            Lavem</placeName> et per ipsum <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Chestnuts #Coloni/tenants" ref="#places/4530"
                            >Battiticzum</placeName>, ubi modo sedent homines vestri et usque in
                            <placeName key="#Landed_possessions #Coloni/tenants" ref="#places/4531"
                            >Ventuvanam</placeName>. Concedo quoque eidem monasterio Sancti Angeli
                        ecclesiam Sancti Angeli de Odaldisci cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terris</rs> et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">servis</rs> et cum omnibus
                        suis pertinentibus, et <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3031">Sancti Benedicti Pictoli</orgName> cum <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiis</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terris</rs> et pertinentibus suis, que ecclesie sunt in Capuam, et
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3058"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Monasteries"
                            >Sanctum Petrum de Scafati</orgName> cum <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasteriis</rs>, <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">servis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et omnibus suis pertinentibus, et
                            <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3060">Sancti Rufi</orgName> cum <rs
                            key="#Coloni/tenants">servis</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terris</rs> et omnibus suis pertinentibus, et <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3061">Sancte Agathe</orgName> sitam prope <rs
                            key="#Walls">muros</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities #Walls" ref="#places/4000">Aversane</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">urbis</rs>, cum <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">hominibus</rs>
                        et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et universis suis
                        pertinentibus, et unum <rs
                            key="#Chestnuts #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >castanetum</rs> optimum et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >terras</rs> pro servitio hospitum que est prope Baptiticzum in <rs
                            key="#Fines">finibus</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Chestnuts #Fines" ref="#places/4528"><geogName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#estates/3028">Sarzani</geogName></placeName>. Omnia prescripta
                        concedo et confirmo perpetualiter prescripto monasterio Sancti Angeli
                        subdito <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancti Benedicti
                            Montis Casini</orgName>, cui <persName key="#Abbots #Personal_rank"
                            ref="#people/2416">Oderisius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> preesse videtur, ab eodem vero abbate ordinatus
                            <persName key="#Prevosts" ref="#people/4216">Girdus</persName> est <rs
                            key="#Prevosts">prepositus</rs> monasterio Sancti Angeli, ad
                        possessionem eiusdem monasterii et dominationem. Quod siquis huius
                        concessionis violator esse presumpserit, <rs key="#Penalty">centum auri
                            optimi libras</rs> persolvat, medietatem eiusdem monasterio eiusque
                        rectoribus et medietatem fisco meo, et soluta hac pena, huius mee
                        concessionis pagina firma et inviolabilis maneat semper. Et ut firmus
                        credatur et diligentius observetur, manu mea subscripsi et meo sigillo feci
                        decorare. Signum domni <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Marquis/duke #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            ref="#people/3002">Iordani</persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">gloriosissimi</rs> principis.
                        IORDANVS. Ex iussione predicti principis scripsi ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Judge" ref="#people/3005">Canzolinus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> in anno principatus ipsius tricesimo primo et
                        vicesimo sexto anno <rs key="#Marquis/duke #Marca/ducatum">ducatus</rs> eius
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/2343"><geogName
                                key="#Marca/ducatum" ref="#estates/3001"
                            >Gaiete</geogName></placeName>. Data sexto kalendas Martii, anno ab
                        incarnatione Domini nostri Iesu Christi .M. LXXX nono. Scriptum <placeName
                            key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capue</placeName> per indictionem
                        duodecimam. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p>Gattola 1734, p. 202-203; <foreign>RSAF</foreign>, pp. 56-59;
